    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65B40 4.0L V8. This high-revving power plant delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, the chassis dynamics remain sharp. Recent preventative maintenance includes a documented rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacement. The suspension retains its original EDC functionality, providing a balanced compression and rebound profile. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the subframe and VANOS system have been inspected and are within spec. A driver\u2019s spec machine for the purist.",
