    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper from highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery remains supple without any rips or significant bolster wear, and it has strictly been a non-smoking environment. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a consistent service schedule. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a firm yet comfortable ride. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring the vehicle is ready for its next owner. This car offers the perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal for those seeking quality without the new-car price tag.",
